(21, 33, 'Audicompendax', NULL, 'SE', 'Stockholm', 'Audio Visual Service Technician', 0, '2018-11-00', '2019-09-00', 'Audiovisual technician.\nProduct fabrication & assembly.\nSystem Testing.\nSmartboard calibration & setup.\nSet up video projection systems, PA systems, and screens.\nComputer system setups & network installation/configuration.\nService & equipment installation, IT support, and accessories repair.\nAV cabling.', '2020-09-10 00:23:34', '2020-09-10 00:23:34'),
(22, 33, 'Self Employed', NULL, 'CA', 'Montreal', 'IT Consultant Film/TV', 0, '1999-12-00', '2014-12-00', 'Various years 1986 - Ongoing\nI have been involved in the IT side of many films as a combination of other roles that I have held due to my technical background. This meant combining both networking and computer technician roles with media production allowing the productions to flow smoothly and be able to deliver the material for shots as intended.\nThe Fixer | TV Mini-Series, Muse Entertainment (2014)\nRED 2 | Feature Film, DC Entertainment (2013)\nSERIE 2 | TV Series, Casablanca Prod. (2012)\nSatan\'s School for Girls | TV Movie, ABC-Spelling Television (2000)\nIT Consultant\nVideo & interactive content creation and playback.\nPC & MAC computer configuration & repair.\nInternet configuration & network issue resolution.\nContent backup.\nComputer selection.\nFTP setup.', '2020-09-10 00:25:04', '2020-09-10 01:11:50'),
(23, 33, 'AVTEC', NULL, 'CA', 'Montreal', 'Audio Visual Technician', 0, '1995-03-00', '1996-06-00', 'Audiovisual technician and client support for corporate and event driven presentations.\nSet up slide and video projection systems, PA systems and screens.\nArrange microphone and perform audio recordings.\nSet stage lighting.\nSimultaneous translation system setups.\nVideo recording, editing and when necessary, duplication of materials. Computer system setups & network installation/configuration.\nService & equipment installation for guest speakers and provide IT support.\nAV cabling.\nEquipment and accessories repair.', '2020-09-10 00:26:14', '2020-09-10 00:26:14'),
(24, 33, 'Concordia University AV Department - Downtown, Loyola, Fine Arts', NULL, 'CA', 'Montreal', 'Audio Visual Technician', 0, '1997-09-00', '2001-04-00', 'Provided a large range of IT and department-specific tasks including equipment and software training.\n\nSet up slide and video projection systems, PA systems & screens.\nArrange microphones and perform audio recordings.\nVideo recording, editing, and when necessary, duplication of materials.\nComputer system setups & network installation/configuration.\nService & equipment installation for guest speakers and provide IT support.\nComputer upgrading, builds, configuration, optimization, networking.\nPhotography darkroom operation, maintenance & Instruction.\nReprovit operation & Instruction. Video editing deck operation, maintenance & Instruction.\nWorkshop instruction in Adobe graphics, video, audio, and media production techniques.\nSound studio operation, maintenance & instruction.\nSound recordist, editor, mixer for film using both magnetic tape & digital synchronization.\nHardware and facility maintenance. AV cabling.\nEquipment and accessories repair.\nClient reception.', '2020-09-10 00:30:19', '2020-09-10 00:30:19'),
(25, 33, 'Concordia University Media Labs', NULL, 'CA', 'Montreal', 'Media Labs Technician & Instructor', 0, '1999-08-00', '2001-02-00', 'Media Labs technician.\nWorkshop Instructor.\nStudio instructor.\nCable and machine maintenance & reparation.\nPhoto Studio & Darkroom Processing.\nProject recording.\nSound Editing.\nComputer Networking.\nBookings.\nSoftware & Equipment planning.', '2020-09-10 00:39:13', '2020-09-10 00:39:54'),
