(28, 33, 'Phillips Lighting Division', NULL, 'CA', 'London Ontario', 'Media Cart Designer', 0, '1991-07-00', '1991-07-00', 'I was hired to create an industrial process recording cart using a high-speed video camera, trolly, and recording deck for evaluating manufacturing processes of its lighting products. I also put together a reference manual and gave operation training of the system to staff and employees.', '2020-09-10 00:43:30', '2020-09-10 00:43:30'),
(29, 33, 'Bell Telecommunications', NULL, 'CA', 'Montreal', 'Level 2 IPTV RT (resolution team) Technician', 0, '2014-05-00', '2015-07-00', 'I delivered IT services as part of Bells resolution team that handled service installation, configuration and issue resolution for business, residential and technical issues of its services, equipment, and communications systems along with onsite Technician installations/servicing.\n\nBoth normal and specialty software-based testing tools were used to troubleshoot and analyze network conditions and potential points of trouble as well as hardware knowledge.\nTechnical support for streaming internet TV.\nBusiness TV & Internet.\nResidential TV & Internet.\nPOS (Point of Sale) Systems.\nService & equipment installation support to technicians.', '2020-09-10 01:00:47', '2020-09-10 01:00:47'),
